# Grind — Your Personal Workout Tracker

## Files
- `index.html` — Main app shell
- `app.js` — All app logic
- `data.js` — Your PPL routine + meal plan
- `manifest.json` — PWA config (for iPhone home screen)
- `vercel.json` — Vercel deployment config

## Deploy to Vercel

### Option A — Vercel Dashboard (easiest)
1. Go to vercel.com → New Project
2. Drag and drop the entire `gymapp` folder
3. Click Deploy — done, you'll get a URL like `grind.vercel.app`

### Option B — Vercel CLI
```bash
npm i -g vercel
cd gymapp
vercel
```

## Add to iPhone Home Screen
1. Open the Vercel URL in Safari (must be Safari)
2. Tap the Share button (box with arrow)
3. Scroll down → tap "Add to Home Screen"
4. Name it "Grind" → tap Add
5. It opens full screen like a real app

## Features
- Today's workout auto-loaded based on day of week
- Log weight + reps per set
- Automatic rest timer (1:30) after each set
- PR detection — alerts when you beat your best
- Workout timer with start/pause/finish
- Meal logging with protein tracker
- Calorie intake + burned logging
- Weekly summary — sessions done, missed, PRs, protein averages
- Weight progress chart per exercise
- All data saved locally on your phone